* Iron Raptor smiled only more at Nightstrike's taunting, bracing herself.*

" Why don't you come down here and find out?"

* She laughed*

" I'm wounded, weak and the fluid loss is getting to my head, might as well 
finish what you started!"

* Then she opened her arms ( what was left of one ), and gestured for 
Nightstrike to come down.
< Let him come, Prowl. But get behind him if he does come.>
